<div class="com-share" data-id="12852" data-title="《Chinajoy 上有个 Cosplay 比赛，选手们都还蛮拼的》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12852/medium/12852.jpg?1438308374" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12852.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
